Access token is the token generated by Access token API which is the Authorization token needed to access other APIs.  The Authorization type used here is OAuth 2.0 authorization.  The Access token API needs following parameters:  grant_type -> "client_credentials" client_id -> {{client_id}} specific to client credentials. client_secret -> {{client_secret}} specific to client credentials. redirect_uri -> {{redirect_uri}} scope -> "root" Response of the API:  "access_token": access token specific to client credentials. "token_type": "Bearer" "expires_in": 86400 This access token valid for 24 hours.
